      "content": "i checked and i'm at 110 right now which is pretty normal. i'm just really nervous about it dropping while im asleep bc i've had bad lows before. if i skip the basal just for tonight, wouldnt that be the safest way to guarantee i don't bottom out? it's only one night and i didnt really eat much to process anyway.",
